metadata.name: Morgana.
metadata.description:
My piece that was displayed on Times Square New York during the 2022 NFT NYC. One of my biggest achievements within the space. This art piece sums up my journey, from the start of creating flyers and artworks for local festivals fifteen years ago to being displayed at the epicenter of the world.

I have been waiting for a special moment to release this artwork. It felt fitting to release this after the release of the “warbb.” short documentary about my journey thus far.

Get your piece of warbb history!
